function slateMe(character) local shirt = character:FindFirstChild("Shirt") local pants = character:FindFirstChild("Pants")
if (shirt ~= nil) then shirt:Remove() end if (pants ~= nil) then pants:Remove() end
local c = character:GetChildren() for i=1,#c do if (c[i].className == "Part") then c[i].Material = Enum.Material.Slate c[i].BrickColor = BrickColor.new(38) end if (c[i].className == "Humanoid") then c[i].WalkSpeed = c[i].WalkSpeed * .9 c[i].MaxHealth = 150 end end end

Tool.Enabled = false Tool.GripForward = Vector3.new(0,-.759,-.651) Tool.GripPos = Vector3.new(1.5,-.35,.1) Tool.GripRight = Vector3.new(1,0,0) Tool.GripUp = Vector3.new(0,.651,-.759)
DrinkSound:Play() DrinkSound:Remove() wait(3)
StoneSound:Play() local h = Tool.Parent:FindFirstChild("Humanoid") if (h ~= nil) then slateMe(h.Parent) else return end
Tool.GripForward = Vector3.new(-.976,0,-0.217) Tool.GripPos = Vector3.new(0.1,0,.1) Tool.GripRight = Vector3.new(.217,0,-.976) Tool.GripUp = Vector3.new(0,1,0)
wait(1)
